sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant LS as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant Milvus as Milvus<br/>gRPC/HTTP
    participant TrustyFMS as TrustyAI FMS<br/>HTTPS
    participant LMEval as TrustyAI LM-Eval<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Search as Brave/Tavily Search<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OTEL as OTEL Collector<br/>4318/TCP HTTP

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 1: Inference Request (via vLLM)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP 8321 (plaintext, platform handles TLS/auth)
    LS->>vLLM: Forward inference request<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000, API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Inference response
    LS->>PG: Store inference record<br/>PostgreSQL 5432, Username/Password
    PG-->>LS: Stored
    LS-->>Client: Chat completion response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 2: RAG Query (Vector I/O + Inference)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/vector-io/query<br/>HTTP 8321
    LS->>vLLM: Generate embedding<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000, API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Embedding vector
    LS->>Milvus: Similarity search<br/>gRPC/HTTP, Token + TLS
    Milvus-->>LS: Matching documents
    LS->>vLLM: Inference with context<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000, API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Augmented response
    LS->>PG: Store results<br/>PostgreSQL 5432
    LS-->>Client: RAG response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 3: Agent Turn (with Tool Execution)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/agents/turn<br/>HTTP 8321
    LS->>vLLM: LLM reasoning<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000, API Token
    vLLM-->>LS: Tool call decision
    LS->>Search: Execute web search<br/>HTTPS 443, API Key
    Search-->>LS: Search results
    LS->>vLLM: LLM with tool results<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000
    vLLM-->>LS: Final response
    LS->>PG: Persist agent state<br/>PostgreSQL 5432
    LS-->>Client: Agent turn response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 4: Safety Check
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/safety/run-shield<br/>HTTP 8321
    LS->>TrustyFMS: Content safety check<br/>HTTPS, TLS
    TrustyFMS-->>LS: Safety evaluation result
    LS-->>Client: Shield response

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 5: Model Evaluation (LM-Eval)
    Client->>LS: POST /v1/eval/run<br/>HTTP 8321
    LS->>LMEval: Submit evaluation job<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    LMEval->>vLLM: Evaluate model<br/>HTTP/HTTPS 8000, API Token
    vLLM-->>LMEval: Model outputs
    LMEval-->>LS: Evaluation results
    LS-->>Client: Eval results

    Note over Client,OTEL: Flow 6: Telemetry Export
    LS->>OTEL: Export traces/metrics<br/>HTTP OTLP 4318
